{"id":232964082,"title":"#Kobe Bryant #R.I.P #集中哀悼","content":"NBA球星柯比布萊恩（Kobe Bryant）被譽為NBA史上最偉大的球員之一，根據外媒《TMZ》報導，美國時間26日，他搭乘的私人直升機驚傳墜毀在加州洛杉磯的卡拉巴斯薩城（Calabasas），享壽41歲，機上的5名乘客也當場去世。\n\n另外《CNN》也報導，當地消防隊早上10點接到消息，趕至現場後發現5人身亡，老婆不在直升機上。\n柯比布萊恩生於美國費城，效力於湖人隊20年，曾獲得5個NBA總冠軍，2016年4月宣布退休，2018年曾和動畫師合作《親愛的籃球》，獲得第90屆奧斯卡最佳短片獎。\n\n看到從小追的球星不幸身亡，真的是無比難過，還有他的周邊要準備炒了🥺","excerpt":"NBA球星柯比布萊恩（Kobe Bryant）被譽為NBA史上最偉大的球員之一，根據外媒《TMZ》報導，美國時間26日，他搭乘的私人直升機驚傳墜毀在加州洛杉磯的卡拉巴斯薩城（Calabasas），享壽","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"14f573f5-3f02-4821-8e18-f561d7b7db91","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-26T20:48:29.594Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-26T21:01:38.087Z","commentCount":54,"likeCount":836,"tags":["HIDE_THUMBNAIL"],"topics":["追星","NBA","KobeBryant"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"追星","forumAlias":"entertainer","school":"LLLLLLLL","department":"fm","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":668},{"id":"514c2569-fd53-4d9d-a415-bf0f88e7329f","count":158},{"id":"011ead16-9b83-4729-9fde-c588920c6c2d","count":4},{"id":"4b018f48-e184-445f-adf1-fc8e04ba09b9","count":3},{"id":"e8e6bc5d-41b0-4129-b134-97507523d7ff","count":2},{"id":"aa0d425f-d530-4478-9a77-fe3aedc79eea","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":false,"withVideos":false,"media":[],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[],"postAvatar":""}